snippet.title: Prison Boss VR | UploadVR Showcase (2023)
snippet.description:
Get Prison Boss VR NOW on PlayStation VR 2! And don’t forget: you’re not just doing time, you’re doing business! https://store.playstation.com/concept...

Prison Boss VR is a crafting and simulation game with one simple goal: make cash! Locked up in your prison cell, produce and sell contraband items to buy your freedom back. But don’t get caught by the guards! 

Crafting at night… 
Roll cigarettes, fill up bottles, write erotic letters, and more! Be sure to stash your goods well, or they will be snatched by the guards! 

…Trading during the day
Cash in on your illegal handiwork by selling it to your fellow inmates. You can also complete special jobs to earn reputation along with useful rewards! 

Are you hard boiled enough to become Prison Boss?

#PrisonBossVR #PSVR2 #VRgame

🐔 Follow the latest news on Prison Boss: Prohibition on X:
